{"tid":1055541,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"碧咸花了3萬購買Y-3波鞋及外套","createTime":"2019-03-10T15:24:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T00:05:03.000Z","uid":222190,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9852de797beb2b0541ca88ddd6285f7b507dad45","tid":1055541,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:24:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LNQZwmw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLNQZwmw.png&h=26e7b459&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5OAKHtb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5OAKHtb.png&h=71e8c5fe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qh97FeS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqh97FeS.png&h=dd9bf2e5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgEGKGy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgEGKGy.png&h=5e7e6644&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日下午5時許，碧咸在數名保鑣陪同下抵達銅鑼灣百德新街Fashion Walk一間服裝店，引來過百途人圍觀。《蘋果》記者見碧咸一入店內即試鞋及試衫，雖然門外有過百人圍觀及舉手機拍照，但碧咸表現大方任影唔嬲，見他雙手放在身後四圍巡視揀衫，甚至當眾脫下黑色上衣，只穿白色底衫試衫，其間有fans跟他揮手，碧咸都有報以微笑和揮手，表現極為親民。短短15分鐘，碧咸已火速掃了4對鞋及數件外套，據知，碧咸是次花了3萬多元購物。"},{"pid":"91dbe10374a6bad41309da652d218d90cd9b4238","tid":1055541,"uid":222190,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:27:05.000Z","msg":"如果連登仔用幾百銀買到Y-3 <br />\n你叫碧咸情何以堪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd495925e21ebb3150fe4d894b2d7e88459d0fde","tid":1055541,"uid":158977,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:34:44.000Z","msg":"佢嗰件&ldquo;白色<span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;底衫&rdquo;</span>&rdquo; 令我諗起呢張：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JuBekmc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJuBekmc.png&h=3be27302&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aefaf0eb457da74dda38dbe1a4c360efbe7d3410","tid":1055541,"uid":204309,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"